1277
01:37:31,791 --> 01:37:33,382
They live in huts now
because of me?

1278
01:37:33,458 --> 01:37:35,791
- I am not saying that.
- Forget it.

1279
01:37:38,398 --> 01:37:41,060
It is so many days, and instead
