1327
01:41:09,774 --> 01:41:14,405
- Go! I don't need you.
- First get down.

1328
01:41:15,414 --> 01:41:17,405
If I get down,
everyone will go down.

1329
01:41:17,483 --> 01:41:20,816
You, that Guru, your
industrialist friend, all of them.

1330
01:41:25,424 --> 01:41:28,825
Go inside and cry,
